<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="idb92ad5c5-47c4-11f1-9a61-b1559996dfe8"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on title 18, U.S.C., 1940 ed., § 485 (<ref href="/us/act/1909-03-04/ch321/s294">Mar. 4, 1909, ch. 321, § 294</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/35/1146">35 Stat. 1146</ref>).</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A minor verbal change was made.</p>
</note>
